All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, LayerInfo
public class LayerInfoImpl
extends BaseLayerInfo

this class defines a LayerInfoImpl that is common to both FeatureServer and ImageServer, for all Layers produced by FeatureServer, and for all sub-Layers produced by ImageServer. Note that this class is *not* used for an ImageServer's group layer.
